</ul>
<p><a name="Lettering_styles" id="Lettering_styles"></a></p>
<h3><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Japanese_writing_system&amp;action=edit&amp;section=12" title="Edit section: Lettering styles">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Lettering styles</span></h3>
<ul>
<li><a href="/wiki/Shodo" title="Shodo" class="mw-redirect">Shodō</a></li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Edomoji" title="Edomoji">Edomoji</a></li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Mincho" title="Mincho" class="mw-redirect">Minchō</a></li>
